<P>
Dead Ahead: The Grateful Dead has canceled three scheduled Labor Day weekend 
shows at the Shoreline Amphitheatre in Mountain View, Calif., in the wake of 
the drug-related death of keyboard player Brent Mydland last month. 
</P>
<P>
