stable condition after being hit when bullets slammed through the wall of her 
South-Central Los Angeles home. Police said they knew of no motive. ; Photo, 
Franklin vallecillo holds a portrait of niece, Jacqueline Aguilera Jose Galvez 
/ Los Angeles Times 
</P>
