chosen to be a liar. . . . We pray to God that the two sides will not clash, 
because if they do, thousands of Americans whom you have pushed into this dark 
tunnel will go home in shrouded coffins.' -- SADDAM HUSSEIN, in a letter to 
Bush ; Photo, 'I think it's clear that what we need to do at this point is to 
enforce the international law. The statements at the United Nations from many 
countries really say it all. So there's no point in me responding.' -- 
PRESIDENT BUSH, in response to Hussein's comments 
</P>
