<BYLINE>
<P>
By Mark Landsbaum and David Reyes 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
THE HUNTED: The late Andrija Artukovic of Seal Beach, a convicted Nazi war 
criminal whose treatment by the Justice Department is being investigated by the 
FBI (A1), is not the only Orange County resident to have faced such charges. . 
. . Bruno Karl Blach of La Habra, who was extradited seven months ago, remains 
in a West German prison, says his attorney, Ronald Parker. No decision has been 
made on whether to charge Blach, who is accused of murdering concentration camp 
prisoners. 
</P>
