with former Archbishop Eugene Marino led to his downfall, said she married the 
prelate in 1988 in a ceremony he performed. At an Atlanta news conference with 
L.A. attorney Gloria Allred, right, Long added: "I love him and . . . stand by 
him." Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
