EMPLOYEE THEFTS; ST JOHN, JUANITA; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS -- WAGES 
AND SALARIES; EMPLOYEE MISCONDUCT; MISUSE OF PUBLIC FUNDS; BRADLEY, TOM; TASK 
FORCE FOR AFRICA LOS ANGELES RELATIONS 
</P>
