<TEXT>
<P>
The value of nonresidential building permits was off 17% from last year for the 
first five months of the year, the most recent period for which information is 
available. There were some increases, though, in the five major building 
categories: the value of permits issued for both industrial buildings and 
stores increased from last year's totals. 
</P>
