seconds off personal best in 3,000-meter pursuit. ; Photo, (Orange County 
Edition) Geoff Ballon works out at the San Diego Velodrome in Balboa Park. Free 
lessons are given at the facility in hopes of developing Olympians. BARBARA 
MARTIN PINHERO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
