<P>
Photo, Ijaz ul-Haq, son of former Pakistan ruler Gen. Zia ul-Haq, prepares to 
address a rally at a mosque in Islamabad today commemorating the second 
anniversary of his father's death in a mysterious plane crash. Agence 
