<TEXT>
<P>
David Keith, who acted in "An Officer and a Gentleman" and "Lords of 
Discipline," is branching out as a singer in a country music band. 
</P>
<P>
Keith, 36, will make his debut next week in his hometown of Knoxville with his 
Hard Country band, which he said has a "traditional, Appalachian hillbilly beat 
. . . but with electric guitars turned up just a little bit." 
</P>
